{SECT 0 {PARA 256 "" 0 "" {TEXT 263 15 "Hong, Sunghyuck" }}{PARA 0 "" 
0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 179 "Save your current w
orksheet as work02-yourlastname.mws.  Remember to save frequently to a
void losing data in case that the system would shut down in the middle
 of a work session! " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "
" {TEXT -1 104 "In the text mode (click on the cap T button) place you
r name(s) and date at the top of your worksheet.  " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
{TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 531 "1.  Basic Manipulations.
  We can use Maple to manipulate algebraic expression as well as to pe
rform arithmetic calculations.  The intent is to learn some basic Mapl
e syntax, while observing some of the neat features of a Computer Alge
bra System (CAS).  We will also review some basic concepts from arithm
etic.   Perform the following calculations with Maple.  As you do thes
e exercises enter notes and comments onto your worksheet in text mode.
  Note the usage of operators +,-,*,/,^,!  and the usage or non-usage \+
of parentheses.  " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
{TEXT -1 60 "Let the following variables represent algebraic expressio
ns:" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 6 "1. \+
   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "f := x^3-x^2-2*x" "6#>%\"fG,(*$%\"xG\"\"$\"\"\"*$
F'\"\"#!\"\"*&F+F)F'F)F," }{TEXT -1 11 "      2.   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "g
 := 6*x^3+11*x^2+6*x+1" "6#>%\"gG,**&\"\"'\"\"\"*$%\"xG\"\"$F(F(*&\"#6
F(*$F*\"\"#F(F(*&F'F(F*F(F(F(F(" }{TEXT -1 22 "                 3.   \+
" }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "h := x^3-5*x+x^2-5;" "6#>%\"hG,**$%\"xG\"\"$\"\"\"*&
\"\"&F)F'F)!\"\"*$F'\"\"#F)F+F," }{TEXT -1 19 "                   " }}
{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 6 "4.    " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "F := x^4-1" "6#>%
\"FG,&*$%\"xG\"\"%\"\"\"F)!\"\"" }{TEXT -1 22 "                5.    \+
" }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "G := 3*x^4+4*x^3-2*x^2+x-6;" "6#>%\"GG,,*&\"\"$\"\"
\"*$%\"xG\"\"%F(F(*&F+F(*$F*F'F(F(*&\"\"#F(*$F*F/F(!\"\"F*F(\"\"'F1" }
{TEXT -1 14 "         6.   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "H := 2*x^2+3*x-2" "6#>%\"
HG,(*&\"\"#\"\"\"*$%\"xGF'F(F(*&\"\"$F(F*F(F(F'!\"\"" }{TEXT -1 24 "  \+
                      " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{EXCHG 
